{"id":160008,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/global-voices-埃及：前总统封锁網絡遭罚款/","date":"2011-06-11T02:30:48Z","modified":"2011-06-11T02:30:48Z","title":"Global Voices | 埃及：前总统封锁網絡遭罚款","content":"<p><p>埃及前总统穆巴拉克（Hosni Mubarak）在先前反政府革命期间，曾经瘫痪国内網絡及手机服务，埃及法院为此于5月28日宣布，将对他和其他官员罚款埃及币5.4亿镑（9000万美元）。</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Hosni_Mubarak_2003.jpg\"><img title=\"Former Egyptian President Hosni Mubarak. Image by Agência Brasil (Creative Commons Atribuição 2.5 Brasil).\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/Hosni_Mubarak_2003.jpg\" alt=\"Former Egyptian President Hosni Mubarak. Image by Agência Brasil (Creative Commons Atribuição 2.5 Brasil).\" width=\"167\" height=\"258\" /></a></p>\n<p>埃及前总统穆巴拉克，照片来自Agência Brasil，依据创用CC BY 2.5授权使用</p>\n</div>\n<p>革命于1月25日开始后，穆巴拉克政权<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/01/25/egypt-twitter-blocked-as-demonstrations-continue/\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/01/25/egypt-twitter-blocked-as-demonstrations-continue/\">首先封锁Twitter</a>，隔天禁止使用<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/01/26/egypt-after-twitter-facebook-now-blocked/\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/01/26/egypt-after-twitter-facebook-now-blocked/\">Facebook</a>，后于1月28日<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/01/28/egypt-an-internet-blackhole/\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/01/28/egypt-an-internet-blackhole/\">封锁所有網絡连线</a>。</p>\n<p>对于罚款一事，以下是民众在公民媒体上的部分反应。</p>\n<p>阿拉伯联合酋长国专栏作家Sultan Al Qassemi在Twitter上<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/SultanAlQassemi/status/74439444526153728\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/SultanAlQassemi/status/74439444526153728\">指出</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>半岛电视台报导，埃及前总统穆巴拉克等人因为在革命期间切断網絡及手机服务，遭罚款9000万美元。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>罚款令部分埃及民众感到困惑，有些人还开始计算，究竟有多少钱会落入自己的口袋。</p>\n<p>Mohammed Hamdy<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/Mody_On/status/74435718189039616\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/Mody_On/status/74435718189039616\">好奇</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>我们会从这9000万美元里拿到多少钱？服务商是否会补偿我们的损失？还是所有钱都由商人收下？</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Mohammed Yousif<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/JawazSafar/status/74439809065693184\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/JawazSafar/status/74439809065693184\">提到</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>这项判似乎是依据财务损失，他应该为授权杀人及禁止紧急服务受审判。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>埃及律师兼“阿拉伯人权资讯网络”执行长Gamal Eid<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/gamaleid/status/74443822452572160\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/gamaleid/status/74443822452572160\">认为</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>我们的控告对象为电讯公司，指控他们是杀害埃及抗争民众的共犯，除非他们能拿出文件证明清白。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Soup\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%85:Soup\">Soup</a></div>\n<p><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/amira-al-hussaini/\" title=\"文章导读 Amira Al Hussaini\">Amira Al Hussaini</a> · 译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/leonard/\" title=\"文章导读 Leonard\">Leonard</a> </span> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/05/28/egypt-mubarak-fined-for-internet-blackout-during-revolution/\" title=\"阅读原文 [en]\">阅读原文 [en]</a> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2011/06/07/9255/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E5%9F%83%E5%8F%8A%EF%BC%9A%E5%89%8D%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%B0%81%E9%94%81%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E9%81%AD%E7%BD%9A%E6%AC%BE&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F06%2F07%2F9255%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F06%2F07%2F9255%2F&#038;desc=%E5